# Florsovivexa App Architecture

This Flutter app follows a clean architecture approach with three layers:
- **Presentation Layer**: UI components and screens
- **Domain Layer**: Business logic and use cases
- **Data Layer**: Data storage and repositories

## Key Development Rules
1. Use setState for state management (no complex state management libraries)
2. Use shared_preferences for data storage
3. Do not use freezed package or part syntax
4. Do not use external image assets (no assets/images/ directory)
5. Do not use cached_network_image package
6. No account functionality required
7. Use system fonts only (no custom fonts)

## App Theme
- Primary brand color: #44D7D0 (teal)
- Dark theme focused with black, deep blue, and coral teal colors
- Language: Chinese